<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" version="2.0"><channel><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link><description>界面快报</description><docs>http://www.rssboard.org/rss-specification</docs><generator>python-feedgen</generator><image><url>https://res.jiemian.com/assets/wap/common/img/jm-new-logo.png</url><title>界面快报</title><link>https://jiemian.com/</link></image><lastBuildDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:00:02 +0800</lastBuildDate><pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:00:02 +0800</pubDate><item><title>湖南华容团洲垸内积水水位累计下降78厘米</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/11414775.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>据央视新闻，湖南华容团洲垸正在加速排涝。截至7月14日18时，团洲垸内水位32.30米，较今日12时下降0.06米、较今日零时下降0.15米，较溃口合龙时（33.08米）累计下降0.78米。</p>
<p>目前，团洲垸累计排水总量3923万方，剩余水量1.8286亿立方。</p>
